{"@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": "Legislation", "legislationType": "StateAdministrativeRule", "legislationJurisdiction": "US-IN", "name": "Indiana - Indiana Administrative Rules (Agentic Discovery) - A1", "identifier": "IN-AGENTIC-A1", "description": "Title 10, ARTICLE 1.5. UNCLAIMED PROPERTY | IARP", "text": "Indiana Administrative Rules and Policies\nHome\nIndiana Register\nAdministrative Code\nMyIAR\nIndiana Administrative Code\nCurrent\nTITLE 10 Office of Attorney General for the State\nARTICLE 1 UNCLAIMED PROPERTY SECTION (REPEALED)\nARTICLE 1.5 UNCLAIMED PROPERTY\nARTICLE 2 CONTRACT APPROVAL\nARTICLE 3 TORT CLAIMS\nARTICLE 4 ATHLETE AGENTS\nARTICLE 5 RELEASE OF SOCIAL SECURITY NUMBERS BY STATE AGENCIES\nARTICLE 6 TOBACCO ENFORCEMENT\nARTICLE 7 TAX SALE BLIGHT REGISTRY (REPEALED)\nTITLE 11 Consumer Protection Division of the Office of the Attorney General\nTITLE 15 State Election Board\nTITLE 16 Office of the Lieutenant Governor\nTITLE 17 Office of Community and Rural Affairs\nTITLE 18 Indiana Election Commission\nTITLE 20 State Board of Accounts\nTITLE 25 Indiana Department of Administration\nTITLE 30 State Personnel Board\nTITLE 31 State Personnel Department\nTITLE 33 State Employees' Appeals Commission\nTITLE 35 Board of Trustees of the Indiana Public Retirement System\nTITLE 40 State Ethics Commission\nTITLE 41 Office of Administrative Law Proceedings\nTITLE 42 Office of the Inspector General\nTITLE 45 Department of State Revenue\nTITLE 50 Department of Local Government Finance\nTITLE 52 Indiana Board of Tax Review\nTITLE 55 Indiana Economic Development Corporation\nTITLE 58 Enterprise Zone Board\nTITLE 60 Oversight Committee on Public Records\nTITLE 62 Office of the Public Access Counselor\nTITLE 65 State Lottery Commission\nTITLE 68 Indiana Gaming Commission\nTITLE 70 Indiana Horse Racing Commission\nTITLE 71 Indiana Horse Racing Commission\nTITLE 75 Secretary of State\nTITLE 80 State Fair Commission\nTITLE 85 Budget Agency\nTITLE 100 Departmen